attributes.twitter: https://twitter.com/laurabaileyvo '''Laura Bailey''' (born May 28, 1981) is an American actress and singer She provides voices for a number of English-language versions of Japanese anime films and television series as well as voice roles in cartoons and video games.In ''Game of Thrones: A Telltale Games Series'', she voices Gwyn Whitehill.==Credits==Telltale Game Series Credits
